UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der schwarze König wird aus seinem Versteck gejagt und unbarmherzig verfolgt.","Ein Damenopfer und ein krönender Bauer eröffnen eine zwingende Jagd.","Dame schlägt auf g7 – Beginn eines erzwungenen Matts."],"en":["The black king is chased from its hideout and pursued without respite.","A queen sacrifice and a crowning pawn open a forcing chase.","Queen takes on g7 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Crni kralj je istjeran iz skrovišta i progonjen bez predaha.","Žrtva dame i pješak koji se kruni otvaraju prisilnu hajku.","Dama uzima na g7 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:007.029' AND BookFileName IN ('chessable-u5-49690.pgn','1001 Deadly Checkmates_firstkey.pgn');
UPDATE BookPuzzles SET HintsJson='{"de":["Der weiße König ist auf den Rand gedrängt und seine Bauern bieten kaum Schutz.","Ein Damenopfer und eine Umwandlung mit Schach starten eine erzwungene Jagd.","Dame schlägt auf g2 – Auftakt zu einem erzwungenen Matt."],"en":["The white king is driven to the edge with its pawns offering little shelter.","A queen sacrifice and a promotion with check begin a forced chase.","Queen takes on g2 — the start of a forced mate."],"hr":["Bijeli kralj je natjeran na rub, a pješaci mu pružaju malo zaklona.","Žrtva dame i pretvorba sa šahom pokreću prisilnu hajku.","Dama uzima na g2 — početak prisilnog mata."]}', HintsVersion=1 WHERE LineId LIKE '%:007.030' AND BookFileName IN ('chessable-u5-49690.pgn','1001 Deadly Checkmates_firstkey.pgn');
